<Layout 
  title="Smart Boards & Interactive Panels in Dubai | LED & LCD Displays | CCTV Monitors | Lovosis Display"
  description="Dubai's leading distributor of Smart Boards, Interactive Panels, CCTV Monitors and Keyboards. Premium LED & LCD display solutions with installation across Dubai and UAE. Call +971 50 916 2488 for consultation."
